<!-- Game Description Table -->

<table class="tablestyle" id="table14" cellspacing="4" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td class="sectional">

<!-- Game Description Header -->
		
		<table class="headertable" id="table15" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="2">
			<tr>
				<td class="headercell">
				<img border="0" src="../../../images/headers/gamedes.jpg" width="240" height="33"></td>
			</tr>
		</table>

<!-- Game Description Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>Flamberge no Seirei (aka Furanbertyu no Seirei) is an adventure game that was released for Playstation and PC.
                  <br><br>In the game the player takes the role of a Shepherd called Kane (the player can change the characters name) that goes inside a cave one day following a stray lamb, there he breaks a jar kicking it accidentally. That jar contains some spirits that were sealed there by the Flamberge kingdom evil prince 100 years ago. There he also find the kingdom princess named Charlotte that was kidnapped by bandits as he saved her the king tell him that she will marry her and will become the prince of the land.
                  <br><br>He will have 3 years to find allies that help him in his quest of becoming the champion that the land needs and be appreciated for the princess (that at the beginning is not so much happy of have to marry him). During the game he will meet different characters (most of them female) that maybe will help him depending of the answers that the player choose during the game.
                  <br><br>The game features japanese voices, different endings and an unlockable character image gallery.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Manufacturer's description:</u><br>
                  <br>Set in the kingdom Furanberuju, novel style adventure game drew a strange destiny of Cain was a hero of the husband for Princess Charlotte. Distinctive encounters with girls, or get input from the territory of which the girls will continue to develop in various ways. Become a princess bridegroom will be developed after three years than any given territory Dorunei.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Features:</u><br>
			<ul><li>First person perspective.</li>
			<li>2D graphics</li>
			<li>Cartoon graphics</li>
			<li>Medieval Fantasy, Anime & Romance themes.</li></ul>
</td>

	</tr>
	</table>
	       	</td>
     </tr>
</table>  

